"\n          ",["P",{"class":"detail-skill-desc"},"The Damage the Hero takes ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"-80%"]," at the start of the battle. Each time the Hero take Damage, the Damage mitigation effect will be reduced by ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"8%"],", with Resistance increased by ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"20%"]," and Damage dealt increased by ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"10%"]," (stackable up to ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-bold text-amber-400"},"16 layers"],"), effective until the end of the battle."],"\n        "],"\n        ",["DIV",{"class":"detail-skill"},"\n          ",["DIV",{"class":"detail-skill-header"},"\n            ",["SPAN",{"class":"detail-skill-id"},"SKILL 5"],"\n            ",["SPAN",{"class":"detail-skill-type"},"Additional Attack"],"\n            ",["SPAN",{"class":"detail-skill-range"},"Range 3"],"\n          "],"\n          ",["P",{"class":"detail-skill-target enemy"},"1 Random Enemy"],"\n          ",["P",{"class":"detail-skill-desc"},"Arthur wields his sacred sword; after a normal attack, ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"50%"]," chance to deal ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"700%"]," Physical Damage to ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-bold text-white bg-slate-700/50 px-1 rounded mx-0.5"},"1"]," random enemy squads within the valid range. ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"40%"]," of this damage will be used to restore the troop power of ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-bold text-white bg-slate-700/50 px-1 rounded mx-0.5"},"2"]," random friendly squads. After casting the Sword in the Stone, ",["SPAN",{"class":"font-black text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-1 rounded"},"50%"]," chance to apply it to the enemy's mid or back-row squad once additionally."],"\n        